</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<ul>
<li>userDetails:需要跟新的实体类对象</li>
<li>&ldquo;phone"：根据表中的列名称进行跟新</li>
<li>userDetails.getPhone():称更新实体类对象的唯一值</li>
<li>&ldquo;avatarname"，"username"：需要更新的列名称</li>
</ul>


